{"tid":2329063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周小龍賣社運藝術品 《文匯》屈宣「獨」","createTime":"2020-12-17T03:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T04:14:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0afb3841e0c410842b9db9eefb2f2a6df0b12209","tid":2329063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/EE47VC42IZBYRFE4CQT7SK73EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FEE47VC42IZBYRFE4CQT7SK73EU%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=0418421a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FEE47VC42IZBYRFE4CQT7SK73EU%2F&h=dad6853e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/EE47VC42IZBYRFE4CQT7SK73EU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n周小龍賣社運藝術品<br />\n《文匯》屈宣「獨」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dwlyyJ-_gYVpZo_HN6Dx6tj5uUw=/1608x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QX5K3WBMGZCBVCC5TIY73EFIJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdwlyyJ-_gYVpZo_HN6Dx6tj5uUw%3D%2F1608x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQX5K3WBMGZCBVCC5TIY73EFIJY.jpg&h=902d9186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Chickeeduck新店遭建制報狙擊，周小龍強調沒有賣含煽動意味的產品。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】連鎖童裝品牌Chickeeduck在多間分店擺放「民主女神像」而遭終止租約等方式打壓後，該店本月再於天后開設藝術生活百貨店，售賣多款與社會運動相關產品，包括「香港人」燙章、迷你版民女像及「手足同行玻璃杯」等。集團行政總裁周小龍形容天后分店屬「希望店」，提醒香港人要撐到最後。惟新店甫開張即遭建制報章狙擊，指控該店涉宣「獨」煽暴，恫嚇或觸犯國安法，周回應時強調店內並無任何產品含煽動意味。<br />\n<br />\n天后興發街的Chickeeduck藝術生活百貨昨開幕，周小龍稱天后店面積約200呎，除售賣品牌T-shirt等產品外，更多是本地藝術家或同路人製作的產品，包括多款「香港主題」的燙章，如「香港人」、「手足」、「兄弟爬山」等，亦有5cm民主女神像擺設、手足同行玻璃杯，以及多款油畫包括《洗腦人》、《國教人》及《千手人》等。另亦有出售柳俊江的《元朗黑夜》、戴耀廷《愛與和平&mdash;未完的抗爭之旅》及《陳健民獄中書簡》等書籍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x0gEoY0_PIjv3ynvRaK0FRKDs04=/1384x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LDUTVBUWSJE5PNTD4JFO4PXDL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx0gEoY0_PIjv3ynvRaK0FRKDs04%3D%2F1384x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLDUTVBUWSJE5PNTD4JFO4PXDL4.jpg&h=fd4b392a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■店內售賣水樽、玻璃杯及T-shirt等產品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提醒港人撐到最後<br />\n<br />\n周稱該店試業約一星期，已獲不少同路人支持，「好多地方都唔敢擺同路人啲產品賣，我希望呢間舖可以提供一個平台」。他又形容該店是「希望店」，提醒港人不要放棄，撐到最後，「有人話我咁樣係送頭，我唔係想扮偉大，自己只是盡做生意人本份」。<br />\n<br />\n惟新店甫開張即受建制針對，。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c98c0c85101bdc8f8bce7ade4311f1e8018fb9d7","tid":2329063,"uid":24688,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"想食饅頭都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e578840bef3f5caf7b8c5415febeed1bad39fb1","tid":2329063,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c98c0c85101bdc8f8bce7ade4311f1e8018fb9d7","tid":2329063,"uid":24688,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"想食饅頭都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4653863c20206813985bb790d90afa7ce218e9a6","tid":2329063,"uid":139606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcf512a3374c8114e2dbdafce385a7fb9f2ca46","tid":2329063,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}